{"msg":{"list":[{"title":null,"userName":"奥古斯塔","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/wbKdib81ny6ic8hPq6WhALCpZNd5Licic1qwBQCtt6DFicMG7jozs0rIn4eD4Fic3RKMklqPNRSeRZiawJYmYPn4w7vpSPz5FWIpG5l/0","content":"1.观察细节：琢磨老板的意见和神情，大概是对自己报告哪部分开始变脸色？老板最不认同哪一点？\n2.侧面了解：重新看自己的报告，和同事交流一下；问老板：是不是报告不够详细还是用词不够严谨？\n3.正面了解：问老板：你想要达到什么效果？对报告有什么不满意的地方？我应该注重哪部分的修改？","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":7009,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490962636000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"寒子","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-31","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay51LC8HCDuYJSWhCiaGfzmy3VbcicUnvJZlFqenDgwRweEhJT3NUuHcdKOrfibQdiaxPrT2cZX8r6hsT/0","content":"思考：\n1.老板想要改善会议流程的真正原因是什么？难道只是提高会议效率吗？\n老板的真正需求一般都是公司利润的提高。\n通过观察老板在看到哪一部分时不满意，来猜测；同时侧面了解最近公司发生的可能影响老板的重要事情，是否有业务下滑，客户减少等情况；还可以直接问老板哪个地方做的不够好，来推断出老板的真正需求。\n2.老板的需求还可以通过提升业务量，扩大公司经营范围等等方式实现。\n3.我可以在报告中深挖改善会议流程与这些关键业务之间的关系，譬如通过改善流程能减少会议时间，提高工作效率，提升业务量，拓展新的市场。以此方式来满足老板的需求。\n","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6871,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490962470000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"史自力","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/siaKjia9aBPcJHOCEV6z4Ay8CYiaFWibYsq0TUGzGLj6UOnQ45ibnxbp7iampXdnR0icJEtGrzWs09JJyRehKQG4LSf9mmdaefdPBwS/0","content":"询问老板哪里令老板不满意？不满意的原因是什么？他想要一个什么样的报告，这份报告包含哪些需求，什么格式写出来更合适？什么时间完成！","voteCount":0,"commentCount":0,"submitId":6825,"type":11,"voteStatus":0,"publishTime":1490884691000,"priority":0,"perfect":null,"problemId":null,"authorType":null,"isMine":null,"labelList":null,"picList":[]},{"title":null,"userName":"Atia文晨#十点睡姑娘#","submitUpdateTime":"2017-03-30","headImage":"http://wx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/PiajxSqBRaEJq5lCFCpXV5RnEdFWCCCiaKDBWIQp8FlrjfAdWoaHcZOcmMmZj0ZqicLVVHdPBiaNG1F2lVdWvXwbXQ/0","content":"通